------------------------DATA FORMATS------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Res Templates :: same as the Appiled JOBS expect, res template name, desc etc will be like for example :: [{"name" : "template example name", "desc": "ssadas", "details": [{section:"Bulltien", details : { "tech": "anglaurjs", "version": "v1", "desc": "blah blkah bakh" }]  }

Appiled jobs --- structure is different  like  [{section:"Bulltien", details : { "tech": "anglaurjs", "version": "v1", "desc": "blah blkah bakh" }]
Appiled jobs Database Table : Columns :: date, company name, desc, user name, others, json data [that is above json data] 

Edited content ;; for example:: we edited the angularjs ::p1:v1 : <desc>

main / standard content :: Tech :: section : versions

------------------------DATA FORMATS------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
